~~~~~ Bukkit Plugin Generator for *nix (inc OSX) systems ~~~~~

Special thanks to tomsik68 for the original.
And sly for first port to *nix

Instructions:

    OSX
    - Run create from terminal, you may need to chmod +x the file
    - Copy the resulting directory into your project directory/

    Linux
    - Run create from a shell, you may need to chmod +x the file
    - Copy the resulting directory into your project directory/

    Windows
    - Run create.bat from windows explorer
    - Copy the resulting directory into your project directory/
